    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7749527/" class="title-link">人，为什么活着</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7749527"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/65728288/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u65728288-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/65728288/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">杨曼婷。</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-01-25"
      class="main-meta">2016-01-25 20:08:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7749527_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  人们所能理解的故事有一定的固定模式—开头、情节、高潮、结尾。 然而，真正的人生，故事忽然开始，忽然结束，不一定有矛盾冲突，也未必有高潮和结局。  林欣浩，男。自由撰稿人。喜欢读书，相信一切外表高深的知识都要遵守简单的逻辑，希望能用最浅白的话讲清楚最复杂的道理。...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7749527/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
