              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/39000408/" class="">第151页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/syloveyangying/" class=" " title="水妖">水妖</a>
                (人生若只如初见)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="39000408">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们追求个人幸福的最高境界，不可能是纵欲，而是内心的平静。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-09-08 00:56</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>我们追求个人幸福的最高境界，不可能是纵欲，而是内心的平静。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

